ue havia sobrado".£— As Grandes Batalhas de Kamigawa_#',NULL,'#_"Cuando el kami que atacó salvajemente Reito aplastó al ejército enemigo, una miríada de pequeños kami invadió el campo de batalla para consumir los restos."£—Grandes batallas de Kamigawa_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('79248','Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit','CHK','Legendary Creature — Goblin Shaman','R','{2}{R}{R}','4','1','1',NULL,'{T}: Ben-Ben, Akki Hermit deals damage to target attacking creature equal to the number of untapped Mountains you control.','#_Some akki thought of Ben-Ben as a kami of trickery in disguise. They hunted for him in the maze of warrens, often falling prey to his traps._#',NULL,'Greg Staples','157','2.685',NULL,'R',NULL,'0.19','0.48','1.25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','恶鬼贤者班班',NULL,'Ben-Ben, ermite akki','Ben-Ben, Akki-Einsiedler','Ben-Ben, Eremita Akki','悪忌の隠者、ベンベン','Ben-Ben, Eremita Akki',NULL,'Ben-Ben, ermitaño akki',NULL,'传奇生物～精灵／祭师',NULL,'Créature légendaire : gobelin et shamane','Legendäre Kreatur — Goblin, Schamane','Creatura Leggendaria — Sciamano Goblin','伝説のクリーチャー ― ゴブリン・シャーマン','Criatura Lendária — Xamã Goblin',NULL,'Criatura legendaria — Chamán trasgo',NULL,'{T}：恶鬼贤者班班对目标进行攻击的生物造成伤害，其数量等同于由你操控且未横置之山脉的数量。',NULL,'{T} : Ben-Ben, ermite akki inflige à la créature attaquante ciblée un nombre de blessures égal au nombre de montagnes dégagées que vous contrôlez.','{T}: Ben-Ben, Akki-Einsiedler fügt einer angreifenden Kreatur deiner Wahl Schadenspunkte in Höhe der Anzahl der ungetappten Gebirge, die du kontrollierst, zu.','{T}: Ben-Ben, Eremita Akki infligge a una creatura attaccante bersaglio un danno pari al numero di Montagne STAPpate che tu controlli.','{T}：攻撃クリーチャー１体を対象とする。悪忌の隠者、ベンベンはそれに、あなたがコントロールするアンタップ状態の山の総数に等しい点数のダメージを与える。','{T}: Ben-Ben, Eremita Akki causa uma quantidade de dano à criatura alvo atacante igual ao número de Montanhas desviradas que você controla.',NULL,'{T}: Ben-Ben, ermitaño akki hace daño a la criatura atacante objetivo igual a la cantidad de montañas enderezadas que controles.',NULL,'#_有些恶鬼觉得班班的真实身分是诈术之神。他们在洞穴迷路间追杀班班，一路上落入其陷阱者不知凡几。_#',NULL,'#_Les akki commençaient à croire que Ben-Ben était un kami de tromperie déguisé. Ils le chassaient dans le dédale de terriers et tombaient souvent dans ses pièges._#','#_Manche Akki hielten Ben-Ben für einen verkleideten Kami der Gaunereien. Sie jagten ihn in den Irrgärten ihrer Bauten, nur um regelmäßig Opfer seiner Fallen zu werden._#','#_Alcuni akki pensavano che Ben-Ben fosse un kami ingannatore sotto mentite spoglie. Gli diedero la caccia nel labirinto di garenne, cadendo spesso vittime delle sue trappole._#','#_悪忌の中には、ベンベンを詐欺の神の化身だと考えていた者もいた。彼らは住処の迷路の中で彼を探し回ったが、ほとんどは彼の罠の餌食となった。_#','#_Alguns dos akkis pensavam que Ben-Ben era um kami da travessura disfarçado. Eles o caçaram no labirinto dos viveiros, caindo com freqüência em suas armadilhas._#',NULL,'#_Algunos akki creían que Ben-Ben era un kami del engaño disfrazado. Lo cazaron por los laberintos de los barracones, cayendo a menudo en sus trampas._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('50451','Blessed Breath','CHK','Instant — Arcane','C','{W}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target creature you control gains protection from the color of your choice until end of turn.£Splice onto Arcane {W} #_(As you cast an Arcane spell, you may reveal this card from your hand and pay its splice cost. If you do, add this card''s effects to that spell.)_#',NULL,NULL,'Tsutomu Kawade','1','3.202','£6/7/2013: You reveal all cards you intend to splice at the same time. Each individual card can be spliced only once onto any one spell.£6/7/2013: A card with a splice ability can’t be spliced onto itself because the spell is on the stack (and not in your hand) when you reveal the cards you want to splice onto it.£6/7/2013: You choose all targets for the spell after revealing cards you want to splice, including any targets required by the text of any of those cards. You may choose a different 